To be able to develop the project and easily to add new features, we needed to pick a framework to work with. 
We started the project with Express.Js and wrote some basic code without a login functionality. 
To start the project you need:

1- Express.js ( read the package.Json)
2-MongoDb

To install and start the project use the command :

npm start
you have to have mono

